<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><id>https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=57&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0</id><title>HKDiscuss money</title><updated>2025-08-05T08:39:38.313129+00:00</updated><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=57&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0"/><generator uri="https://lkiesow.github.io/python-feedgen" version="1.0.0">python-feedgen</generator><subtitle>Latest articles</subtitle><entry><id>6c53f297b0ea344d0183ec20710dea0a</id><title>今日受黑雨影響。會暴升500點。</title><updated>2025-08-05T13:03:48+08:00</updated><author><name>代號666</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-05T13:03:48+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573486374"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573486374"&gt;預計。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31999500&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11439934976891c34a79d266_55496912"/><published>2025-08-05T13:03:48+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>f74976c0b04b3d966388ee10d54fd29e</id><title>香港經濟｜標普全球7月香港PMI升至49.2、連續6個月低於50 營商景氣下滑趨緩</title><updated>2025-08-05T13:04:56+08:00</updated><author><name>katewells</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-05T13:04:56+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573486387"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573486387"&gt;踏入下半年，標普全球7月份香港採購經理指數（PMI）由上月的47.8回升至49.2，連續6個月低於50，顯示營商環境連續6個月轉差，惟倒退幅度已縮減至期內最小。&lt;br&gt;7月PMI維持於50持平線下，主因新增訂單量持續萎縮。隨着本土和全球經濟走弱，影響內外銷情，故整體訂單量連續6個月縮減，惟跌幅尚算適中。從海外和中國內地新接的業務量繼續急速下滑，兩者跌幅都與上月相若。企業於是在7月減產，其緊縮速度較上月放緩，偏於溫和，走勢與整體新訂單一致。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://inews.hket.com/article/3988714/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F" target="_blank" uhash="fc040dd54be9e66f1b7272d4e1f3d1c3"&gt;https://inews.hket.com/article/3988714/香港經濟&lt;/a&gt;｜標普全球7月香港PMI升至49.2、連續6個月低於50%E3%80%80營商景氣下滑趨緩&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31999502&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11439934976891c34a79d266_55496912"/><published>2025-08-05T13:04:56+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>47023e190676f8216c5039e3ea2291dc</id><title>🚬🐸點解炒牛熊咁撚屎？仲成日出post真係冇撚用呢個21哥</title><updated>2025-08-05T13:15:24+08:00</updated><author><name>破馬會操盤強人</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-05T13:15:24+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573486515"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573486515"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16412872" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573486515" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250805/20250805_393583494073edb1886a8j425JwimFBk.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/c5e443/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250805/20250805_393583494073edb1886a8j425JwimFBk.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16412872_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16412872&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;mobile_1.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (216.73 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-5 13:16&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16412873" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" styl